our relationship,

36:11.036 --> 36:15.572
and I feel like this will
help you understand why.

36:17.476 --> 36:19.142
♪ Let's start a riot ♪

36:19.144 --> 36:21.578
ealize,
like, they're not
talking (bleep)--

36:21.580 --> 36:23.046
