Kelsey, Madisson.

38:03.882 --> 38:05.415
Like, I just can't
get a break.

38:05.417 --> 38:07.984
There's nothing I can do.
It's Chloe. If you don't--

38:07.986 --> 38:10.086
Why don't you
say something?
If you don't get--

38:10.088 --> 38:12.756
Why don't you go up to Chloe
and Cara and say something?

38:12.758 --> 38:14.858
I think she's playing Cara
like a pawn,

38:14.860 --> 38:16.059
movin' her around
her chessboard.

38:16.061 --> 38:18.161
And here you are,
sticking up for Cara.

38:18.163 --> 38:19.496
(sighs)

38:19.498 --> 38:21.398
You sleep
with Cara recently?

38:21.400 --> 38:22.499
♪♪

38:22.501 --> 38:23.633
