Chloe's done this

38:42.888 --> 38:44.521
with me and whoever
I was with.

38:44.523 --> 38:45.889
Like, she's tried
to sabotage

38:45.891 --> 38:48.091
literally every relationship
I've been in.

38:48.093 --> 38:50.060
Okay, I know.
Poor you.

38:50.062 --> 38:52.829
There's something
that happened in the past

38:52.831 --> 38:54.597
that I didn't want to
have to ever tell you

38:54.599 --> 38:56.566
because I was hoping
it would go away.

38:56.568 --> 38:59.002
What?

38:59.004 --> 39:01.938
♪♪

39:06.278 --> 39:08.678
But I didn't want
to have to ever
bring this up again.

39:08.680 --> 39:10.680
Like, Chloe's an
old friend of mine

39:10.682 --> 39:13.583
and I don't know
if it's revenge,

39:13.585 --> 39:18.121
but Chloe told me
that I'm the guy

39:18.123 --> 39:20.657
that she wants to spend
the rest of her life with,

39:20.659 --> 39:23.793
and that she's
in love with me.

39:23.795 --> 39:26.363
I really think that
she wishes that

39:26.365 --> 39:28.264
she was in
your position.

39:28.266 --> 39:29.999
Are you serious?

39:30.001 --> 39:31.501
Yeah, I'm serious.
When?

39:31.503 --> 39:33.069
A few years back.

39:33.071 --> 39:36.172
Like, don't you think
that's something
you should tell me?

39:36.174 --> 39:37.273
Juliette--

39:37.275 --> 39:38.641
Did you sleep with her?

39:38.643 --> 39:40.043
No!
What?

39:40.045 --> 39:41.444
♪♪

39:41.446 --> 39:43.113
Is she getting in between
our relationship? Yes.

39:43.115 --> 39:44.781
Why is she getting
in between our relationship?

39:44.783 --> 39:46.516
Probably that.
Probably 'cause
she's jealous.

39:46.518 --> 39:50.887
That makes so much sense,
like, throughout the years.
I don't really--

39:50.889 --> 39:52.956
♪♪

39:52.958 --> 39:55.825
You're in no position to,
like, settle down.

39:55.827 --> 39:58.361
That's the problem.

39:58.363 --> 39:59.963
Did you sleep
with Amanda?

39:59.965 --> 40:01.598
I mean,
I wasn't gonna tell you,

40:01.600 --> 40:02.732
but like all that
(bleep) went down.

40:02.734 --> 40:04.634
I can't believe
you want to be

40:04.636 --> 40:06.069
