and (bleep) her.

40:06.071 --> 40:09.172
He's cheated on you
so many times.

40:09.174 --> 40:11.307
She was, like,
all over Alex,

40:11.309 --> 40:12.976
biting his cheek...

40:12.978 --> 40:15.178
Don't you want to be
with a guy

40:15.180 --> 40:16.513
that chases you?

40:16.515 --> 40:18.548
Yeah.

40:18.550 --> 40:20.984
Why didn't you
tell me this before?

40:20.986 --> 40:22.752
