our relationship,

40:24.389 --> 40:27.657
and I feel like this will
help you understand why.

40:29.895 --> 40:31.394
But, like, I don't want
to allow her

40:31.396 --> 40:32.962
to get in between
you and I.

40:32.964 --> 40:34.063
And, like,
it's not fair to us--

40:34.065 --> 40:36.232
Chloe's gone way
too far this time.

40:36.234 --> 40:38.168
♪♪

40:38.170 --> 40:41.104
And somebody has to
do something about it.

40:41.106 --> 40:44.174
♪♪

40:49.181 --> 40:50.814
(Juliette)
This season on "Siesta Key"...

40:50.816 --> 40:52.916
I'll make sure you're
the happiest girl in the world.

40:52.918 --> 40:54.117
(crying)
Oh, it's gorgeous.

40:54.119 --> 40:55.618
We can't let anyone
get between us.

40:55.620 --> 40:59.022
(Madisson)
I'm holding out hope
for me and Ben.

40:59.024 --> 41:01.191
Cheating on you
is my biggest mistake.

41:01.193 --> 41:04.394
(Garrett)
I care about you, obviously.

41:04.396 --> 41:06.095
This bitch,
she's using you.

41:06.097 --> 41:07.397
I don't give a (bleep)
about you.

41:07.399 --> 41:08.565
