using a bi girl.

41:23.615 --> 41:25.181
Are you serious?

41:25.183 --> 41:26.883
(Cara)
Jealousy is
a really awful thing.

41:26.885 --> 41:31.321
Did Alex have sex
with this girl?

41:31.323 --> 41:33.857
